16
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,200
And I knew that he was not of this world, but rather a being from a realm beyond our

17
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,560
own.

18
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,760
One night I decided to confront him.

19
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:08,360
I crept up to the manor, my heart racing with fear and anticipation.

20
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:13,600
As I approached, I heard the sound of laughter, low and menacing, coming from within.

21
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:18,640
