26
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:36,040
The stranger was not a vampire or a demon, but rather a lover come to claim my heart

27
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,560
and soul.

28
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:42,360
And so it was that we embarked on a journey of love and horror, entwined in a tale of

29
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,400
